Deputy President William Ruto has disowned  a group of individuals mobilizing support for his 2022 presidential campaign. Through  his secretary of communications  David Mugonyi…the deputy president said  at no time has he ever approved  a sketchy,messy , premature and political canvassing. West Pokot woman representative Lillian  Cheptoo on Wednesday mobilized a group of youths to campaign for  Ruto’s 2022-2032 bid.  